<bibRefCitation id="EFB94B194C49FFB3FC96FD318B02EA91" author="Garcia-Beltran, J. A." box="[794,1079,690,714]" pageId="0" pageNumber="126" pagination="291 - 296" refId="ref407" refString="Garcia-Beltran, J. A. (2022) Taxonomic and nomenclatural update of Cenostigma (Leguminosae: Caesalpinioideae) in Cuba. Phytotaxa 543 (5): 291 - 296. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 543.5.4" type="journal article" year="2022">García-Beltrán (2022: 294)</bibRefCitation>
