<subSubSection id="C33265634C49FFB3FBB7FD318A3FEB02" pageId="0" pageNumber="126" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B9736E84C49FFB3FBB7FD318A3FEB02" blockId="0.[136,1452,690,858]" pageId="0" pageNumber="126">
includes two varieties: 
<taxonomicName id="4C284D6B4C49FFB3FAA6FD318CEFEAB5" authority="(Britton &amp; P. Wilson 1930: 335) Garcia-Beltran (2022: 294)" authorityName="Garcia-Beltran" authorityPageNumber="294" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Britton &amp; P. Wilson" baseAuthorityPageNumber="335" baseAuthorityYear="1930" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Cenostigma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="0" pageNumber="126" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="pinnatum" variety="savannarum">
<emphasis id="B95CEAFA4C49FFB3FAA6FD318A99EA91" box="[1322,1452,690,714]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="126">C. pinnatum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B95CEAFA4C49FFB3FF36FD548E0BEAB5" box="[186,318,727,750]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="126">savannarum</emphasis>
(Britton &amp; P.Wilson 1930: 335) 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB94B194C49FFB3FD3DFD558CEFEAB5" author="Garcia-Beltran, J. A." box="[689,986,726,750]" pageId="0" pageNumber="126" pagination="291 - 296" refId="ref407" refString="Garcia-Beltran, J. A. (2022) Taxonomic and nomenclatural update of Cenostigma (Leguminosae: Caesalpinioideae) in Cuba. Phytotaxa 543 (5): 291 - 296. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 543.5.4" type="journal article" year="2022">García-Beltrán (2022: 294)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and the typical variety of the subspecies. However, in the combination to the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C284D6B4C49FFB3FDC9FD798DF1EB4A" box="[581,708,762,785]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Cenostigma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="0" pageNumber="126" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B95CEAFA4C49FFB3FDC9FD798DF1EB4A" box="[581,708,762,785]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="126">Cenostigma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
of this last variety, a complete and direct reference to its basonym was not indicated. In this way, 
<taxonomicName id="4C284D6B4C49FFB3FE26FC9D8BEEEB6D" authority="(Urb.) Garcia-Beltran (2022: 294)" authorityName="Garcia-Beltran" authorityPageNumber="294" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Urban" baseAuthorityYear="1900" box="[426,1243,798,822]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Cenostigma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="0" pageNumber="126" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="pinnatum" variety="oblongifolium">
<emphasis id="B95CEAFA4C49FFB3FE26FC9D8DA2EB6D" box="[426,663,798,822]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="126">Cenostigma pinnatum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B95CEAFA4C49FFB3FD42FC9D8C51EB6D" box="[718,868,798,822]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="126">oblongifolium</emphasis>
(Urb.) 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB94B194C49FFB3FC3AFC9D8BEEEB6D" author="Garcia-Beltran, J. A." box="[950,1243,798,822]" pageId="0" pageNumber="126" pagination="291 - 296" refId="ref407" refString="Garcia-Beltran, J. A. (2022) Taxonomic and nomenclatural update of Cenostigma (Leguminosae: Caesalpinioideae) in Cuba. Phytotaxa 543 (5): 291 - 296. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 543.5.4" type="journal article" year="2022">García-Beltrán (2022: 294)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is an invalid name (
<bibRefCitation id="EFB94B194C49FFB3FF03FCC18E52EB01" author="Turland, N. J. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Greuter, W. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Herendeen, P. S. &amp; Knapp, S. &amp; Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Li, D. - Z. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; May, T. W. &amp; McNeill, J. &amp; Monro, A. M. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F." box="[143,359,834,858]" pageId="0" pageNumber="126" refId="ref452" refString="Turland, N. J., Wiersema, J. H., Barrie, F. R., Greuter, W., Hawksworth, D. L., Herendeen, P. S., Knapp, S., Kusber, W. - H., Li, D. - Z., Marhold, K., May, T. W., McNeill, J., Monro, A. M., Prado, J., Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F. (2018) International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code). Regnum Vegetabile 159. Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten. https: // doi. org / 10.12705 / Code. 2018" type="book" year="2018">
Turland 
<emphasis id="B95CEAFA4C49FFB3FF67FCC08E14EB01" box="[235,289,834,858]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="126">et al.</emphasis>
, 2018
</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 41.5). To correct such a nomenclatural mishap here is the validly published name.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
